sequenceDiagram
    participant Student
    participant Django
    participant pgvector
    participant Embedder
    participant LLM

    Student->>Django: Ask question via chat
    Django->>Embedder: POST /embed<br/>{text: "question"}
    Embedder-->>Django: 384-dim vector

    Django->>pgvector: SELECT * WHERE<br/>tenant_id = X<br/>ORDER BY embedding <=> query<br/>LIMIT 5
    pgvector-->>Django: Top 5 matching chunks

    Django->>Django: Build context:<br/>sources + question

    alt LLM Available
        Django->>LLM: Chat completion<br/>(context + question)
        LLM-->>Django: Natural language answer
        Django->>Django: Add citations [1][2][3]
    else Offline Mode
        Django->>Django: Return sources verbatim
    end

    Django-->>Student: Display answer + sources

    Student->>Django: Click citation [1]
    Django-->>Student: Show source document<br/>+ highlighted passage
